## How to use

Import CPP-STRUCT

```cmake
include(cmake-cpp-struct/main.cmake)
```

## Declare Application

```cmake
cppstruct_app(
	MyApp
)
cppstruct_app_headers(
	MyApp
	defines.hpp
)
cppstruct_app_sources(
	MyApp
	main.cpp
)
```

## Declare Static Library

```cmake
cppstruct_lib(
	MyLib1
)
cppstruct_lib_headers(
	MyLib1
	lib1_private.hpp
)
cppstruct_lib_public_headers(
	MyLib1
	lib1.hpp
)
cppstruct_lib_sources(
	MyLib1
	lib1.cpp
)
```